<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.3.3">
<l>aṇṇaṉ māya ṉaṇikoḷcen tāmaraik</l>
<l>kaṇṇaṉ ceṅkaṉi vāykaru māṇikkan</l>
<l>teṇṇi ṟaicuṉai nīrtiru vēṅkaṭat</l>
<l>teṇṇi ṟolpukaḻ vāṉava rīcaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The majesty, the trickster, Kṛṣṇa with decorated red lotus</l>
<l>eyes, the black ruby with a a red fruit mouth</l>
<l>is the lord of the celestials, of countless ancient fame,</l>
<l>on sacred Vēṅkaṭam with the water of clear full mountain pools.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
